{"TopicId":160026,"ForumId":25,"TopicTitle":"The KSC Trucking Challenge","CreatedByName":"HamnavoePer","CreatedById":160271,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-01T09:23:14Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"HamnavoePer","CreatedById":160271,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-01T09:23:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe Challenge? Make and use a semi truck to haul around the trailers in the included save file.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nALL TRAILERS MUST BE MOVED IN ORDER AND TOWED ON THE GROUND \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/106024-gchristopher/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022106024\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/106024-gchristopher/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@gchristopher\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPoints are given for every trailer you manage to move without tipping and \u00A0for how good your truck looks judged by scores below.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe Save:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://drive.google.com/open?id=0B5WzwDcs9MQBbU5Yc0s2eXdlWmc\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://drive.google.com/open?id=0B5WzwDcs9MQBbU5Yc0s2eXdlWmc\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0 The file is titled Truckin\u0027 Challenge.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA video is preferred to make judging easier.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nScoring:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003ETrailer Moving\u003C/strong\u003E:\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo all trailers and park truck without tipping = 30 points\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMove 4 Trailers without tipping = 25 points\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMove 3 Trailers without tipping = 20 points\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMove 2 trailers without tipping = 15 points\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMove 1 trailer without tipping = 10 points\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EThe truck:\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA Big Rig = 15 points\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA European truck (Left\u00A0hand Drive)\u00A0= 15 points\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA Uk Truck (Right\u00A0Hand Drive) = 16 points\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA Truck. (No steering Wheel) = 12 points.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA Right\u00A0hand drive Big Rig\u00A0= 16 points\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA grill = 5 points\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA working exhaust = 5 points\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA light Bar = 5 points\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n8 or more wheels = an extra 5 points\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHave a working engine (Using\u00A0Alternators on jet/rocket engines to create power) = 20 points\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:24px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EExample:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedOther ipsEmbeddedOther_limited\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?app=core\u0026amp;module=system\u0026amp;controller=embed\u0026amp;url=http://imgur.com/gallery/tARCW\u0022 style=\u0022height:482px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis is a Uk truck with electric power. It would be relatively low scoring.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003ELeader Board:\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E1.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E2.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E3.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E4.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E5.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E6.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E7.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E8.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E9.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E10.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:16px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022color:#3498db;\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EGOOD LUCK TO ALL YOU TRUCKERS OUT THERE\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou may want to check the flags \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-05-04T16:17:36Z\u0022 title=\u002205/04/2017 04:17  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EMay 4, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by HamnavoePer\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"MiffedStarfish","CreatedById":175356,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-01T18:48:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223040892\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022160026\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221493630594\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022160271\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022HamnavoePer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 hours ago, HamnavoePer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA Uk Truck (Left Hand Drive) = 16 points\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI could be not thinking, but don\u0027t cars and trucks\u00A0in the UK have right hand steering wheels?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLooks like a fun,\u00A0original challenge. I might\u00A0give it a go later.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HamnavoePer","CreatedById":160271,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-01T18:49:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223041433\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022160026\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221493664524\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022175356\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022MiffedStarfish\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, MiffedStarfish said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI could be not thinking, but don\u0027t cars and trucks\u00A0in the UK have right hand steering wheels?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLooks like a fun,\u00A0original challenge. I might\u00A0give it a go later.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo they do. I should know (Me being scottish an all) oops, Thanks for making me notice that \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Numerlor","CreatedById":174198,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-01T21:02:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy not use docking ports?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HamnavoePer","CreatedById":160271,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-02T15:52:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223041602\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022160026\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221493672556\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022174198\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Numerlor\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n18 hours ago, Numerlor said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy not use docking ports?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI wanted a more articulated truck feel which i don\u0027t think docking ports replicate. And it would make it a lot easier to do the reverse parking on the challenge\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Numerlor","CreatedById":174198,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-02T15:59:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223042459\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022160026\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221493740369\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022160271\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022HamnavoePer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, HamnavoePer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI wanted a more articulated truck feel which i don\u0027t think docking ports replicate. And it would make it a lot easier to do the reverse parking on the challenge\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can\u0027t do challenge with this style because those legs sometimes clip through terrain and it is lower than it is supposed to be so I drag it around. This wouldn\u0027t happen with docking ports\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HamnavoePer","CreatedById":160271,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-02T16:32:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223042467\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022160026\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221493740795\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022174198\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Numerlor\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n31 minutes ago, Numerlor said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can\u0027t do challenge with this style because those legs sometimes clip through terrain and it is lower than it is supposed to be so I drag it around. This wouldn\u0027t happen with docking ports\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSorry but, as i said, the docking ports don\u0027t hinge around freely like it does right now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"gchristopher","CreatedById":106024,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-04T09:22:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022stupid_truck.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://gchristopher.net/kerbal/stupid_truck.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HamnavoePer","CreatedById":160271,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-04T15:59:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223044473\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022160026\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221493889738\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022106024\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022gchristopher\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, gchristopher said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://gchristopher.net/kerbal/stupid_truck.jpg\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022stupid_truck.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 src=\u0022http://gchristopher.net/kerbal/stupid_truck.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI need to update my rules methinks \u263A\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Torquimedes","CreatedById":137645,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-04T20:44:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223042459\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022160026\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221493740369\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022160271\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022HamnavoePer\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 5/2/2017 at 10:52 AM, HamnavoePer said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI wanted a more articulated truck feel which i don\u0027t think docking ports replicate. And it would make it a lot easier to do the reverse parking on the challenge\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFolks have built trailer hitches out of almost-docked ports, allowing rotation but held in place by their magnetic attraction.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/149385-semi-trailer-truck-and-artificial-gravity-module-based-on-docking-ports-stock/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-05-04T20:45:12Z\u0022 title=\u002205/04/2017 08:45  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EMay 4, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Torquimedes\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"gchristopher","CreatedById":106024,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-04T22:18:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis challenge is a little taste of the things people did in the\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/62942-an-affordable-space-program-making-the-reusable-spacecraft-pay-off/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003EAffordable Space Program\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0challenge by \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/78834-sirjoab/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002278834\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/78834-sirjoab/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@SirJoab\u003C/a\u003E. (Which is still my favorite challenge by far.) That covered a broad range of \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E-grounds surface vehicle jobs for refueling and reloading mission payloads.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor a more flexy/stretchy articulated joint, you can use some docking port jr\u0027s in series. Here\u0027s a two-tanker fuel truck that did that. In this case, the fueling arm used\u00A0Infernal Robotics.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/NYyDVD7.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022NYyDVD7.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA claw set to rotate will pivot freely like a ball hitch. This can be used to make sturdy multi-trailer fuel trucks, for example.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s also worth considering \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Attachment System (mod)\u0022\u003EKAS\u003C/abbr\u003E for connections.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf I were to do the whole challenge, I\u0027d definitely use TweakScale for even bigger monster truck wheels!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}